title: Charming & Adorable 2/1 House w/Large Kitchen, Large closet, W/D, Easy
posting_body: ["Adorable and charming two-bedroom garden level unit in Denver's highly prized Capitol Hill neighborhood.", 'You can walk to nearly everything including the best restaurants, coffee shops, brew pubs, gyms, yoga and all the cool things in the neighborhood.', 'This unit proudly offers an amazing hidden oasis in the backyard.', 'Sip your coffee and watch the koi pond flourish.', 'Incredible large kitchen.', 'Historic decorative fireplace.', 'Tons of storage space and large closets.', 'Washer / dryer included.', 'Two off-street parking spaces, a rare find.', 'What more could you ask for?', 'Contact us for more details: Text me at:', 'show contact info', 'PLEAS TEXT ONLY!', 'Thank you!!', '* Available immediately', '* Private entrance', '* 2 off-street parking spaces included!', '* Shared amazing backyard space', '* Washer / dryer included', '* Historic touches', '* Large primary bedroom', '* Walk everywhere in this awesome neighborhood', '*', 'Large closets', '* Well behaved smaller dog and cat allowed with an extra pet fee', '* Tenant pays for their own electric.', 'Gas, water, trash and recycling included.', 'Tenant shovels the snow on their private walk way to their unit.', '* Local and responsive Property Management', '* One year lease minimum', '*', 'No smokers please', '* Not currently accepting applications from more than 2 adults', '* Good credit applicants only.', 'Need a 550 FICO score or higher to schedule a showing.', 'Please know your credit score when calling.', '*', 'Income requirement is 3x the monthly rent', "* Security Deposit equivalent to one month's rent", 'Tenant pays for electric.', 'Water, gas, trash and recycle are included.', 'Tenant shovels snow on pathway next to their unit.']
